 />\n玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c179b13713735040fbaa1d5a174ff1c6763534e","tid":188045,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8804ef7768bcbf33a85088e1984f4ae126701a","tid":188045,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"唔好亂諗咁多啦<br />\n可能你篇文夠特別 marker好欣賞呢<br />\n考完先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3670c89b653d04628ca31ad084a508d778dd15","tid":188045,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好亂諗咁多啦<br />\n可能你篇文夠特別 marker好欣賞呢<br />\n考完先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢題2要求應該係READING 文1咁<br />\n借經歷講體悟<br />\n而唔係背影咁<br />\n已炒"},{"pid":"c40dad7ceea3fb01be0f1c8b67e0bb5cd7696019","tid":188045,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"體會 =\\= 經歷<br />\n<br />\n記敘議論 理應都可以，重點係你有咩感悟，得着，反思，呢d要落重筆墨寫。"},{"pid":"431678a820a7dc7c5fb215542a8d702ba0c27dd2","tid":188045,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>體會 =\\= 經歷<br />\n<br />\n記敘議論 理應都可以，重點係你有咩感悟，得着，反思，呢d要落重筆墨寫。</blockquote><br />\n一段敘一段體會(夾敘夾議)<br />\n頭尾好短講一件事同足印有關做引入，其餘體會<br />\n先記敘後體會<br />\n<br />\n亦該都無問題。"},{"pid":"ebe63ac4ee7f32c95dd6ecb602b9ac80841b51c4","tid":188045,"uid":19800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寫左篇背影式記敘抒情<br />\n無個人<strong>體會</strong><br />\n題已離 卷已炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n記斜抒情點解等於無個人體會？<br />\n唔好嚇自己啦 努力考落去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人